org.drip.analytics.input

Class LatentStateShapePreservingCCIS

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.analytics.input.LatentStateShapePreservingCCIS
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CurveConstructionInputSet

    public class LatentStateShapePreservingCCIS
extends java.lang.Object
implements CurveConstructionInputSet
    LatentStateShapePreservingCCIS contains the Parameters needed for the Curve Calibration/Estimation. It contains the following: - Calibration Valuation Parameters - Calibration Quoting Parameters - Calibration Market Parameters - Calibration Pricing Parameters - Array of Calibration Span Representation - Map of Calibration Quotes - Map of Calibration Measures - Double Map of the Date/Index Fixings - The Shape Preserving Linear Latent State Calibrator Additional functions provide for retrieval of the above and specific instrument quotes.
    Author:
    Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
